      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried different headphones and it still happens. actually it feels a lot more specific than just \"noise.\" like i'll be listening to something chill and suddenly i feel this wave of anxiety or irritation right after a certain beat pattern. it feels like the audio is being used to trigger something. can u look up if there are any known ways companies use infrasound or subliminal frequencies in streaming? i need to know if this is even a real thing people do.",
